                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-crisp-orange mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Interactive Prototypes
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-crisp-orange mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Usability Testing & Optimization
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:p-8">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581291518857-4e27b48ff24e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80" 
                alt="UI/UX design process with wireframes and user flow diagrams"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="lg:p-8 order-2 lg:order-1">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626785774573-4b799315345d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2071&q=80" 
                alt="Brand identity design with logo concepts and color palettes"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 order-1 lg:order-2">
              <div class="inline-block bg-crisp-orange/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-2 mb-4">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-crisp-orange">🏢 Brand Identity</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Visual Brand Identity Design</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Complete brand identity systems that establish your unique visual voice and create memorable impressions across all digital touchpoints.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-crisp-orange mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Logo Design & Variations
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-crisp-orange mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Color Palette & Typography
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-crisp-orange mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Brand Guidelines & Style Guide
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-crisp-orange mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Marketing Material Templates
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Design Tools Section */}
  <div class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-6">Design Tools We Master</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We use industry-leading design tools and software to create professional, pixel-perfect designs.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/photoshop/photoshop-original.svg" alt="Photoshop" class="w-12 h-12 mb-3" />
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Photoshop</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/illustrator/illustrator-plain.svg" alt="Illustrator" class="w-12 h-12 mb-3" />
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Illustrator</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/canva/canva-original.svg" alt="Canva" class="w-12 h-12 mb-3" />
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Canva</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/sketch/sketch-original.svg" alt="Sketch" class="w-12 h-12 mb-3" />
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Sketch</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Design Process Section */}
  <div id="design-process" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-6">Our Design Process</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          From research to final design, we follow a proven methodology that ensures your project exceeds expectations and achieves your goals.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Research & Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Deep dive into your brand, audience, and goals to create a strategic foundation for exceptional design.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Wireframes & Concepts</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Create wireframes and initial concepts to establish information architecture and user flow before visual design.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Visual Design & Prototyping</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Bring designs to life with stunning visuals and interactive prototypes that showcase the final user experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
            4
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Testing & Refinement</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Test designs with real users, gather feedback, and refine the experience for optimal usability and conversion.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Pricing Section */}
  <div class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-6">Web Design Packages</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Choose the perfect design package for your needs. All packages include responsive design, brand guidelines, and design files.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pt-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 flex flex-col">
          <div class="text-center mb-8 flex-shrink-0">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">Essential</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Perfect for startups and small businesses looking to establish their online presence</p>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">From £600</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Starting price</p>
